In this chapter covers how to read stack traces (or call stacks), which is the printout that follows programming errors.


:::: {.column-margin}

Launch app with the [`shinypak` package](https://mjfrigaard.github.io/shinypak/articles/getting-started.html):

:::{style='font-size: 0.65rem;'}
```r 
launch('H_stack-traces')
```
:::
